Future Scope

In the future, the system can be enhanced with real-time seat availability integration, live tracking of buses/trains, automated refund processing, 
AI-based ticket recommendations, multi-language chatbot support for booking assistance, and integration with UPI/Wallet payments. 
The platform can also include predictive maintenance alerts for vehicles and a feedback-driven route optimization system.

Requirement fullfillment 

All core requirements of the system have been fulfilled including ticket booking, seat selection, passenger details capture, automatic ticket generation, 
payment status update, issue reporting, issue assignment, resolution tracking, notification updates, and role-based access for citizen/officer/admin. 
Additional validations and workflow automation have been added to improve accuracy and user experience.
